<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <%- include('partials/head', { title, description }) %>
</head>
<body class="bg-page text-text-primary font-body antialiased overflow-x-hidden">
  <canvas id="dot-grid" class="fixed inset-0 z-0 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></canvas>
  <div id="cursor-glow" class="fixed w-[320px] h-[320px] rounded-full pointer-events-none z-0 opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-300" style="background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(59,130,246,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%); transform: translate(-50%, -50%);" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <%- include('partials/nav') %>

  <main class="relative z-10 pt-20">
    <section class="py-section-sm">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-accent/20 bg-accent/10 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-accent">Free Challenge</span>
          <h1 class="mt-8 text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-display font-black tracking-tight leading-[1.05]">75 Hard AI Challenge</h1>
          <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-xl sm:text-2xl font-display font-semibold tracking-tight text-text-secondary">Build <span class="text-accent-warm/80">real AI fluency</span> in 75 days by following 5 simple rules.</p>
          <p class="mt-5 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">Not another course. A daily commitment with something real to show at the end.</p>
          <p class="mt-8 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-accent">Build <span class="text-text-muted">·</span> Learn <span class="text-text-muted">·</span> Share <span class="text-text-muted">·</span> Connect <span class="text-text-muted">·</span> Grow</p>
          <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-x-3 gap-y-2 text-sm text-text-muted">
            <span>No coding required</span>
            <span aria-hidden="true">·</span>
            <span>No AI background needed</span>
            <span aria-hidden="true">·</span>
            <span>Completely free</span>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
            <a href="#join" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-accent px-8 py-4 text-white font-semibold transition-colors hover:bg-accent-hover" data-magnetic>Join the Challenge</a>
            <a href="#rules" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-border-subtle px-8 py-4 text-text-secondary font-semibold transition-colors hover:border-text-muted hover:text-text-primary">See the Rules</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pb-section-sm">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="glass-card p-10 lg:p-14">
          <span class="inline-block text-xs font-medium text-accent uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-6">Why This Exists</span>
          <div class="max-w-2xl space-y-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">
            <p>Everyone's talking about AI. Most people scroll through the headlines, watch the demos, maybe try ChatGPT a few times... and that's where it ends.</p>
            <p>You've probably thought: <em>I should really learn this stuff.</em></p>
            <p>But then what? You bookmark a bunch of videos you never go back to. You try a tool for 20 minutes and move on. You tell yourself you'll get to it next week.</p>
            <p>Next week never comes. And meanwhile, the gap between people who <span class="font-semibold text-text-primary">actually know AI</span> and people who just <em>talk about</em> AI gets wider every single day.</p>
            <p class="font-bold text-text-primary">The 75 Hard AI Challenge is how you close that gap.</p>
            <p>75 days of showing up. 5 daily tasks. At the end, you'll have a real project, real skills, and <span class="font-semibold text-text-primary">75 days of proof</span> that you actually did it.</p>
            <p>This isn't another course. It's not a tutorial playlist. It's a commitment — and the result is something you can point to and say: <span class="font-semibold text-text-primary"><em>I built that with AI.</em></span></p>
            <p>No coding required. No AI background needed. Just 75 days of doing the work.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="rules" class="pb-section-sm">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="glass-card p-10 lg:p-14">
          <span class="inline-block text-xs font-medium text-accent uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-6">The Problem</span>
          <div class="max-w-2xl space-y-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">
            <p>Every day, AI gets more powerful. Every day, the gap grows between people who use AI and people who just hear about it.</p>
            <p>You know you should be learning this. You've probably tried.</p>
            <p>Maybe you started a course and didn't finish it. Maybe you played with ChatGPT for a week and then forgot about it. Maybe you've been meaning to "get into AI" for months now, but there's always something else going on.</p>
            <p>The problem isn't motivation. The problem isn't intelligence. The problem is that there's no structure, no accountability, and no deadline.</p>
            <p class="font-bold text-text-primary">That's what this challenge gives you.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pb-section-sm">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        <span class="inline-block text-xs font-medium text-accent uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4">The Challenge</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-display font-bold tracking-tight mb-8">What is the 75 Hard AI Challenge?</h2>
        <div class="max-w-2xl space-y-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">
          <p>The 75 Hard AI Challenge is a 75-day structured challenge designed to take you from wherever you are right now to genuine AI fluency — with something real to show for it.</p>
          <p>Every day, you complete 5 simple AI tasks. You do this for 75 days straight. That's it.</p>
          <p>Every task can be done using conversational AI tools — Claude, ChatGPT, Gemini, or whatever you prefer. The AI does the heavy lifting. You show up and direct it.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-8 inline-block rounded-xl border border-accent/20 bg-accent/10 px-6 py-4 text-accent font-semibold">
          The challenge is completely free.
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pb-section-sm">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        <span class="inline-block text-xs font-medium text-accent uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4">The Rules</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-display font-bold tracking-tight mb-10">These are non-negotiable. Every day, all five.</h2>

        <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-5">
          <div class="glass-card p-6" data-tilt>
            <span class="text-accent font-display font-bold text-sm">01</span>
            <h3 class="mt-5 font-display font-bold text-xl">BUILD</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-accent">1 hour</p>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">Work on your AI project.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="glass-card p-6" data-tilt>
            <span class="text-accent font-display font-bold text-sm">02</span>
            <h3 class="mt-5 font-display font-bold text-xl">LEARN</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-accent">10 minutes</p>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">Watch AI video content.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="glass-card p-6" data-tilt>
            <span class="text-accent font-display font-bold text-sm">03</span>
            <h3 class="mt-5 font-display font-bold text-xl">SHARE</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-accent">1 post</p>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">Post about your AI journey.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="glass-card p-6" data-tilt>
            <span class="text-accent font-display font-bold text-sm">04</span>
            <h3 class="mt-5 font-display font-bold text-xl">CONNECT</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-accent">1 person</p>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">Help someone with AI.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="glass-card p-6 sm:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1" data-tilt>
            <span class="text-accent font-display font-bold text-sm">05</span>
            <h3 class="mt-5 font-display font-bold text-xl">GROW</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-accent">1 session</p>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">Use AI for personal development.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 glass-card p-8 lg:p-10">
          <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-5">
            <div class="md:col-span-2">
              <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-accent">Daily Checklist</p>
              <h3 class="mt-4 text-2xl font-display font-bold tracking-tight">Simple rules. Hard because you do them every day.</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="md:col-span-3 grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2">
              <p class="rounded-xl border border-border-subtle bg-page/70 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-text-secondary">1 hour building</p>
              <p class="rounded-xl border border-border-subtle bg-page/70 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-text-secondary">10 minutes learning</p>
              <p class="rounded-xl border border-border-subtle bg-page/70 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-text-secondary">1 public post</p>
              <p class="rounded-xl border border-border-subtle bg-page/70 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-text-secondary">1 person helped</p>
              <p class="rounded-xl border border-border-subtle bg-page/70 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-text-secondary">1 personal growth session</p>
              <p class="rounded-xl border border-accent-warm/30 bg-accent-warm/10 px-4 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-accent-warm">75 minutes for 75 days</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="mt-10 text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">That's it. Five simple rules. One hour, ten minutes, one post, one person, one session.</p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">The rules are straightforward, and each one is explained in depth with examples, ideas, and resources when you join the challenge — so you'll know exactly what to do from Day 1.</p>

        <div class="mt-8">
          <a href="#join" class="inline-flex rounded-xl bg-accent px-8 py-4 text-white font-semibold transition-colors hover:bg-accent-hover" data-magnetic>Join the Challenge — It's Free</a>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-16 space-y-3">
          <details class="faq-item glass-card overflow-hidden">
            <summary class="px-8 py-6 cursor-pointer text-text-primary font-display font-semibold flex justify-between items-center">BUILD — 1 hour per day<span class="faq-icon text-text-muted text-xl leading-none ml-4 shrink-0">+</span></summary>
            <div class="px-8 pb-6 text-text-secondary font-body leading-relaxed space-y-5">
              <p>Pick a project on Day 1. Work on it every day using your AI tool of choice — you direct, the AI builds.</p>
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium text-text-primary mb-2">What can you build?</p>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0"></span><span>A content automation system for your business or niche</span></li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0"></span><span>A prompt library tailored to your industry</span></li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0"></span><span>A resource hub or knowledge base for a community you care about</span></li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0"></span><span>A workflow automation that saves you (or someone else) hours</span></li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0"></span><span>An AI-generated portfolio or visual project</span></li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0"></span><span>An app or web tool — built entirely through conversation with AI</span></li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0"></span><span>Literally anything you can track and build over time</span></li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium text-text-primary mb-2">How does Git work?</p>
                <p class="text-sm">Every day, your progress gets saved publicly to your Git repository. Think of it as your progress photo — your commit history shows every step of the journey. On Day 75, you can scroll from your first commit to your last and see exactly how far you came.</p>
                <p class="text-sm mt-3">Don't know Git? Your AI tool sets it up for you. You tell it "create a repository for my project" and it handles everything. You never touch a single command.</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium text-text-primary mb-2">What counts?</p>
                <p class="text-sm">Anything that shows real progress. Code files, documents, images, prompt templates, configuration files, workflow diagrams. If you're building a prompt library, your daily commit might be three new prompts you tested and refined. If you're building an app, it might be a new feature. The format doesn't matter — the progress does.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="faq-item glass-card overflow-hidden">
            <summary class="px-8 py-6 cursor-pointer text-text-primary font-display font-semibold flex justify-between items-center">LEARN — 10 minutes per day<span class="faq-icon text-text-muted text-xl leading-none ml-4 shrink-0">+</span></summary>
            <div class="px-8 pb-6 text-text-secondary font-body leading-relaxed space-y-5">
              <p>Watch at least 10 minutes of AI-focused video content. Intentionally.</p>
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium text-text-primary mb-2">What counts:</p>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0"></span><span>YouTube tutorials on AI tools and techniques</span></li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0"></span><span>Online course videos (free or paid)</span></li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0"></span><span>Conference talks and keynotes about AI</span></li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0"></span><span>Tool-specific walkthroughs and demos</span></li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0"></span><span>AI news breakdowns and analysis</span></li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium text-text-primary mb-2">What doesn't count:</p>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0"></span><span>Scrolling through short-form AI clips on TikTok or Reels</span></li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0"></span><span>Background listening while doing something else</span></li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0"></span><span>Videos you've already watched</span></li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm">10 minutes is the minimum. It's a low bar on purpose — most people end up watching longer once they start. But even on your busiest day, 10 minutes of intentional learning is non-negotiable.</p>
              <p class="text-sm"><strong class="text-text-primary">Bonus:</strong> Leave a comment on the video sharing one thing you learned. This reinforces your learning, contributes to the creator's engagement, and creates a public trail of your AI education.</p>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="faq-item glass-card overflow-hidden">
            <summary class="px-8 py-6 cursor-pointer text-text-primary font-display font-semibold flex justify-between items-center">SHARE — 1 post per day<span class="faq-icon text-text-muted text-xl leading-none ml-4 shrink-0">+</span></summary>
            <div class="px-8 pb-6 text-text-secondary font-body leading-relaxed space-y-5">
              <p>Pick your platform on Day 1 — LinkedIn, X, Instagram, TikTok, YouTube, a blog — wherever your people are. Post something every day about what you're learning, building, or experiencing.</p>
              <p><strong class="text-text-primary">This is your public accountability.</strong> You're articulating what you actually did — not just consuming. The same people who probably got you interested in AI will now see your real journey. Be real. That's what resonates.</p>
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium text-text-primary mb-2">What counts:</p>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0"></span><span>A text post about what you learned or built today</span></li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0"></span><span>A screenshot of your project's progress with context</span></li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0"></span><span>A short video showing something you built or discovered</span></li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0"></span><span>A thread breaking down an AI concept you just learned</span></li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0"></span><span>A "Day X" update with reflections on the journey so far</span></li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0"></span><span>A tip or technique you discovered while working on your project</span></li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0"></span><span>An honest post about struggling, failing, or being confused — vulnerability performs</span></li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0"></span><span>A before/after of your project (yesterday vs. today)</span></li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium text-text-primary mb-2">What doesn't count:</p>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0"></span><span>Sharing someone else's content without your own perspective</span></li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0"></span><span>A post with nothing to do with AI or the challenge</span></li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0"></span><span>Engagement farming with no substance ("Day 23! Still going!")</span></li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm">Every post includes <span class="font-semibold text-accent">#75HardAI</span> — this is how participants find each other across platforms and how the challenge grows organically.</p>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="faq-item glass-card overflow-hidden">
            <summary class="px-8 py-6 cursor-pointer text-text-primary font-display font-semibold flex justify-between items-center">CONNECT — 1 person per day<span class="faq-icon text-text-muted text-xl leading-none ml-4 shrink-0">+</span></summary>
            <div class="px-8 pb-6 text-text-secondary font-body leading-relaxed space-y-5">
              <p>Every day, help one person with an AI-related question or problem. Online or in person. Publicly or privately.</p>
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium text-text-primary mb-2">What counts:</p>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0"></span><span>Answering a question in the challenge community</span></li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0"></span><span>Responding to someone's AI question on social media (Reddit, X, LinkedIn, Quora)</span></li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0"></span><span>Helping a coworker, friend, or family member with something AI-related</span></li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0"></span><span>Showing someone how to use an AI tool to solve a problem they mentioned — even if they didn't frame it as an "AI question"</span></li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0"></span><span>Jumping into a forum thread where someone is stuck</span></li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0"></span><span>Explaining an AI concept to someone who's curious</span></li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium text-text-primary mb-2">Why this matters:</p>
                <p class="text-sm">Teaching is the fastest way to learn. Every time you explain something to someone else, you deepen your own understanding. By Day 75, you'll have helped 75 people — and you'll understand AI well enough to explain it to anyone.</p>
                <p class="text-sm mt-3">There's a deeper purpose here too. People ask questions every day that could be answered with AI — they just don't know it yet. By training yourself to spot these opportunities, you develop a reflex for seeing AI applications in the real world. By Day 75, you'll be the person everyone comes to.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="faq-item glass-card overflow-hidden">
            <summary class="px-8 py-6 cursor-pointer text-text-primary font-display font-semibold flex justify-between items-center">GROW — 1 session per day<span class="faq-icon text-text-muted text-xl leading-none ml-4 shrink-0">+</span></summary>
            <div class="px-8 pb-6 text-text-secondary font-body leading-relaxed space-y-5">
              <p>This is the rule most people don't expect to love.</p>
              <p>Use your AI as a thinking partner for your actual life. Not for productivity. Not for work. For <em>you</em>.</p>
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium text-text-primary mb-2">What this looks like:</p>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0"></span><span>End your day with: <em>"Here's what happened today — what patterns do you notice in how I handled it?"</em></span></li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0"></span><span>Work through a decision you've been avoiding</span></li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0"></span><span>Ask it to help you reframe something that's been weighing on you</span></li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0"></span><span>Journal with it about what you're grateful for and what you'd do differently</span></li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0"></span><span>Explore your strengths, blind spots, and recurring patterns</span></li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0"></span><span>Have a coaching-style conversation about your goals, fears, or mindset</span></li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0"></span><span>Prep for a difficult conversation or decision</span></li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0"></span><span>Ask it to challenge a limiting belief you've been carrying</span></li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium text-text-primary mb-2">Why this is here:</p>
                <p class="text-sm">Most people think of AI as a productivity tool. This rule teaches you it's also a mirror, a coach, and a sounding board. AI can help you understand yourself better, make better decisions, and show up as a better version of yourself.</p>
                <p class="text-sm mt-3">This is the soul of the challenge. AI fluency is the headline — but becoming a more self-aware, intentional person is the transformation most people don't see coming. By Day 75, this might be the rule that changed you the most.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pb-section-sm">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
